{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-mdx-frontmatter-type-mdx-frontmatter-slug-js-content-file-path-content-docs-responsive-examples-filter-mdx","path":"/docs/filter/","result":{"data":{"mdx":{"id":"fb986b8d-9d74-5032-a44d-55ca3568edec","body":"\r\nimport { Paragraph } from \"../../../src/components/Mdx/textComponents\"\r\nimport CodeWrapper from \"../../../src/components/Mdx/CodeWrapper\"\r\nimport CatImg from \"../../../src/images/cat-resized.png\"\r\n\r\n# Filter\r\n\r\n#### How to use\r\n\r\nThe 4 filters included by default are blur, contrast, grayscale, and saturate. Each of these can be specfied as sm, md, and lg, like paddings and margins for exmaple but with only a few values. While low, md, hi probably make more sense, stayed with sm, md lg just because it's used with so many other things. However, names can be chagned and filters can be added in `variables.scss`, so if don't like the values, or wanted to add a drop-shadow for example, it's totally possible! See the [Customize](/customize/) section for more info.\r\n\r\nThe default filter classes are:\r\n\r\n| Class        | CSS rule                 |\r\n| :----------- | :----------------------- |\r\n| blur-sm      | filter: blur(2px);       |\r\n| blur-md      | filter: blur(4px);       |\r\n| blur-lg      | filter: blur(6px);       |\r\n| contrast-sm  | filter: contrast(0.75);  |\r\n| contrast-md  | filter: contrast(1.25);  |\r\n| contrast-lg  | filter: contrast(1.75);  |\r\n| grayscale-sm | filter: grayscale(0.33); |\r\n| grayscale-md | filter: grayscale(0.67); |\r\n| grayscale-lg | filter: grayscale();     |\r\n| saturate-sm  | filter: saturate(0.5);   |\r\n| saturate-md  | filter: saturate(2);     |\r\n| saturate-lg  | filter: saturate(3);     |\r\n\r\nthese can be prefixed with responsive classes liks `scr:` or `max-tab` like the other classes in this category. Let's jump into some examples!\r\n\r\n### Examples:\r\n\r\nLet's see how these filters alter this photo:\r\n\r\n<div className=\"center p-lg\">\r\n  <figure>\r\n    <img src={CatImg} alt=\"Cat\" />\r\n    <figcaption>\r\n      <Paragraph\r\n        className=\"text-lg py-md align-center\"\r\n        text=\"Origonal Img 512x512\"\r\n      />\r\n    </figcaption>\r\n  </figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div className=\"row gap-lg\">\r\n  <div className=\"col-4\">\r\n    <figure>\r\n      <div className=\"ratio-4/3\">\r\n        <img\r\n          className=\"w-full h-full object-fill blur-sm \"\r\n          src={CatImg}\r\n          alt=\"Cat\"\r\n        />\r\n      </div>\r\n      <figcaption>\r\n        <Paragraph className=\"text-lg py-md\" text=\".blur-sm\" />\r\n      </figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div className=\"col-4\">\r\n    <figure>\r\n      <div className=\"ratio-4/3\">\r\n        <img\r\n          className=\"w-full h-full object-fill blur-md \"\r\n          src={CatImg}\r\n          alt=\"Cat\"\r\n        />\r\n      </div>\r\n      <figcaption>\r\n        <Paragraph className=\"text-lg py-md\" text=\".blur-md\" />\r\n      </figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div className=\"col-4\">\r\n    <figure>\r\n      <div className=\"ratio-4/3\">\r\n        <img\r\n          className=\"w-full h-full object-fill blur-lg \"\r\n          src={CatImg}\r\n          alt=\"Cat\"\r\n        />\r\n      </div>\r\n      <figcaption>\r\n        <Paragraph className=\"text-lg py-md\" text=\".blur-lg\" />\r\n      </figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div className=\"row gap-lg\">\r\n  <div className=\"col-4\">\r\n    <figure>\r\n      <div className=\"ratio-4/3\">\r\n        <img\r\n          className=\"w-full h-full object-fill contrast-sm \"\r\n          src={CatImg}\r\n          alt=\"Cat\"\r\n        />\r\n      </div>\r\n      <figcaption>\r\n        <Paragraph className=\"text-lg py-md\" text=\".contrast-sm\" />\r\n      </figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div className=\"col-4\">\r\n    <figure>\r\n      <div className=\"ratio-4/3\">\r\n        <img\r\n          className=\"w-full h-full object-fill contrast-md \"\r\n          src={CatImg}\r\n          alt=\"Cat\"\r\n        />\r\n      </div>\r\n      <figcaption>\r\n        <Paragraph className=\"text-lg py-md\" text=\".contrast-md\" />\r\n      </figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div className=\"col-4\">\r\n    <figure>\r\n      <div className=\"ratio-4/3\">\r\n        <img\r\n          className=\"w-full h-full object-fill contrast-lg \"\r\n          src={CatImg}\r\n          alt=\"Cat\"\r\n        />\r\n      </div>\r\n      <figcaption>\r\n        <Paragraph className=\"text-lg py-md\" text=\".contrast-lg\" />\r\n      </figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div className=\"row gap-lg\">\r\n  <div className=\"col-4\">\r\n    <figure>\r\n      <div className=\"ratio-4/3\">\r\n        <img\r\n          className=\"w-full h-full object-fill grayscale-sm \"\r\n          src={CatImg}\r\n          alt=\"Cat\"\r\n        />\r\n      </div>\r\n      <figcaption>\r\n        <Paragraph className=\"text-lg py-md\" text=\".grayscale-sm\" />\r\n      </figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div className=\"col-4\">\r\n    <figure>\r\n      <div className=\"ratio-4/3\">\r\n        <img\r\n          className=\"w-full h-full object-fill grayscale-md \"\r\n          src={CatImg}\r\n          alt=\"Cat\"\r\n        />\r\n      </div>\r\n      <figcaption>\r\n        <Paragraph className=\"text-lg py-md\" text=\".grayscale-md\" />\r\n      </figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div className=\"col-4\">\r\n    <figure>\r\n      <div className=\"ratio-4/3\">\r\n        <img\r\n          className=\"w-full h-full object-fill grayscale-lg \"\r\n          src={CatImg}\r\n          alt=\"Cat\"\r\n        />\r\n      </div>\r\n      <figcaption>\r\n        <Paragraph className=\"text-lg py-md\" text=\".grayscale-lg\" />\r\n      </figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div className=\"row gap-lg\">\r\n  <div className=\"col-4\">\r\n    <figure>\r\n      <div className=\"ratio-4/3\">\r\n        <img\r\n          className=\"w-full h-full object-fill saturate-sm \"\r\n          src={CatImg}\r\n          alt=\"Cat\"\r\n        />\r\n      </div>\r\n      <figcaption>\r\n        <Paragraph className=\"text-lg py-md\" text=\".saturate-sm\" />\r\n      </figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div className=\"col-4\">\r\n    <figure>\r\n      <div className=\"ratio-4/3\">\r\n        <img\r\n          className=\"w-full h-full object-fill saturate-md \"\r\n          src={CatImg}\r\n          alt=\"Cat\"\r\n        />\r\n      </div>\r\n      <figcaption>\r\n        <Paragraph className=\"text-lg py-md\" text=\".saturate-md\" />\r\n      </figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div className=\"col-4\">\r\n    <figure>\r\n      <div className=\"ratio-4/3\">\r\n        <img\r\n          className=\"w-full h-full object-fill saturate-lg \"\r\n          src={CatImg}\r\n          alt=\"Cat\"\r\n        />\r\n      </div>\r\n      <figcaption>\r\n        <Paragraph className=\"text-lg py-md\" text=\".saturate-lg\" />\r\n      </figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nHere is the html for the Saturate row to provide a working example:\r\n\r\n<CodeWrapper title=\"HTML\" >\r\n\r\n```HTML\r\n<!-- the <img> tags recieve the object-fit classes: -->\r\n<div class=\"row gap-lg\">\r\n  <div class=\"col-4\">\r\n    <figure>\r\n      <div class=\"ratio-4/3\">\r\n        <img\r\n          class=\"w-full h-full object-fill saturate-sm \"\r\n          src=\"static/cat-resized-2ec747eea85cbd774bc0c06734ec57d8.png\"\r\n          alt=\"Cat\"\r\n        />\r\n      </div>\r\n      <figcaption>\r\n        <p class=\"text-lg py-md\">.saturate-sm</p>\r\n      </figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"col-4\">\r\n    <figure>\r\n      <div class=\"ratio-4/3\">\r\n        <img\r\n          class=\"w-full h-full object-fill saturate-md \"\r\n          src=\"static/cat-resized-2ec747eea85cbd774bc0c06734ec57d8.png\"\r\n          alt=\"Cat\"\r\n        />\r\n      </div>\r\n      <figcaption>\r\n        <p class=\"text-lg py-md\">.saturate-md</p>\r\n      </figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"col-4\">\r\n    <figure>\r\n      <div class=\"ratio-4/3\">\r\n        <img\r\n          class=\"w-full h-full object-fill saturate-lg \"\r\n          src=\"static/cat-resized-2ec747eea85cbd774bc0c06734ec57d8.png\"\r\n          alt=\"Cat\"\r\n        />\r\n      </div>\r\n      <figcaption>\r\n        <p class=\"text-lg py-md\">.saturate-lg</p>\r\n      </figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n```\r\n\r\n</CodeWrapper>\r\n\r\nAnd of course these are all responsive. Here's a responsive exmaple that changes filter on screen width, if you're in a browser you can resize to see it react to the default breakpoints (might have to close the sidebar on smaller withs)\r\n\r\n<div className=\"center p-lg\">\r\n  <figure>\r\n    <img\r\n      className=\"w-full h-full \r\n\t\t\t\tlg:contrast-lg\r\n\t\t\t\tscr:saturate-lg\r\n\t\t\t\ttab:grayscale-lg\r\n\t\t\t\tblur-lg\r\n\t\t\t\"\r\n      src={CatImg}\r\n      alt=\"Cat\"\r\n    />\r\n    <figcaption>\r\n      <Paragraph\r\n        className=\"align-center text-lg display-none radius-md lg:display-block\"\r\n        text=\"Break Point: lg Filter: contrast-lg\"\r\n      />\r\n      <Paragraph\r\n        className=\"align-center text-lg display-none scr:display-block lg:display-none\"\r\n        text=\"Break Point: scr Filter: saturate-lg\"\r\n      />\r\n      <Paragraph\r\n        className=\"align-center text-lg display-none tab:display-block scr:display-none\"\r\n        text=\"Break Point: tab Filter: grayscale-lg\"\r\n      />\r\n      <Paragraph\r\n        className=\"align-center text-lg display-block tab:display-none\"\r\n        text=\"Break Point: tab Filter: blur-lg\"\r\n      />\r\n    </figcaption>\r\n  </figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nThat does it for filters. Happy coding!\r\n","frontmatter":{"description":"Overview of Filter","title":"Filter","type":"docs","image":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"fb986b8d-9d74-5032-a44d-55ca3568edec","frontmatter__type":"docs","frontmatter__slug":"filter","__params":{"frontmatter__type":"docs","frontmatter__slug":"filter"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Filter","tags":["responsive","box-sizing"],"type":"docs","description":"Overview of Filter","category":"responsive","slug":"filter","order":150}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2241216091"],"slicesMap":{}}